-- Staging layer: 1:1 with returns table

    SELECT
        return_id,
        item_id,

-- int_approved_returns.sql
```sql
-- Intermediate layer: deduplicate to one approved return per item
WITH source AS (
    SELECT
        return_id,
        item_id,
        return_date,
        reason,
        status,
        ROW_NUMBER() OVER (
            PARTITION BY item_id
            ORDER BY status DESC, return_date DESC
        ) AS row_num
    FROM {{ ref('stg_returns') }}
)
SELECT
    item_id,
    return_date,
    status
FROM source
WHERE row_num = 1 AND status = 'approved'
```

-- int_items_with_returns.sql
```sql
-- Intermediate layer: join items with return status
WITH source AS (
    SELECT
        oi.item_id,
        oi.order_id,
        oi.product_id,
        CASE WHEN ar.item_id IS NOT NULL THEN 1 ELSE 0 END AS is_returned
    FROM {{ ref('stg_order_items') }} oi
    LEFT JOIN {{ ref('int_approved_returns') }} ar
        ON ar.item_id = oi.item_id
)
SELECT
    item_id,
    order_id,
    product_id,
    is_returned
FROM source
```

-- int_products_with_categories.sql
```sql
-- Intermediate layer: enrich products with category names
WITH source AS (
    SELECT
        p.product_id,
        p.name,
        COALESCE(c.name, '(unknown)') AS category_name
    FROM {{ ref('stg_products') }} p
    LEFT JOIN {{ ref('stg_categories') }} c
        ON c.category_id = p.category_id
)
SELECT
    product_id,
    name,
    category_name
FROM source
```

-- fct_product_return_rates.sql
```sql
-- Mart layer: final return rates by category
WITH items_with_categories AS (
    SELECT
        iwr.item_id,
        iwr.is_returned,
        pc.category_name
    FROM {{ ref('int_items_with_returns') }} iwr
    LEFT JOIN {{ ref('int_products_with_categories') }} pc
        ON pc.product_id = iwr.product_id
)
SELECT
    category_name,
    COUNT(item_id) AS total_items_sold,
    SUM(is_returned) AS total_items_returned,
    ROUND(SUM(is_returned) * 100.0 / COUNT(item_id), 2) AS return_rate
FROM items_with_categories
GROUP BY category_name
ORDER BY return_rate DESC
